OL,4,CPlans to modernise power of attorney
OL,5,Csystem
OL,6, Ministers are looking to overhaul the
OL,7, legal process for people to nominate
OL,8, someone to take financial and health
OL,9, decisions on their behalf if they lose
OL,10, the ability to act for themselves.
OL,12,FThere are more than five million
OL,13,Fregistered Lasting Powers of Attorney -
OL,14,For LPAs - in England and Wales.
OL,16,FBut there are concerns the system is
OL,17,Ftoo slow and difficult to use.
OL,19,FUnder the current paper-based
OL,20,Fapplication process, it can taken
OL,21,Fmonths for powers to be handed over.
